1.  Migrate specificationtools classes into expressiontools.
    Then remove specificationtools. Then change expressiontools to specificationtools.
    The result will be a single package.

2.  Implement the following set methods:
        set_aggregate()
        set_articulations()
        set_dynamics()
        set_marks()
        set_markup()
        set_pitch_class_transform()
        set_registration()
        set_tempo()

3.  Implement a method to slur leaves by divisions.
    Implement general methods to span leaves by divisions.

4.  Add tests to show counttime component select expression score-evaluation
    that respects time-relation settings.
